com.commeto.kuleuven.MP.dataClasses

Class HTTPResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.commeto.kuleuven.MP.dataClasses.HTTPResponse

  • public class HTTPResponse
extends java.lang.Object
     Created by Jonas on 4/03/2018.

 Class to bundle the information gotten from a HTTP response message and the id that might have
 been specified.

 Attributes:
  - responseCode      Response code of the HTTP response.
  - responseMessage   Response message of the HTTP response
  - responseBody      Body of the HTTP response.
  - id                Id of the LocalRoute getting uploaded or updates.
